text.section:
A nursing home shall give each new or prospective resident the following written information about the family council:
The name, address, and phone number of a current member of the family council;
A brief description of the purpose and function of the family council;
Instructions on how the resident or prospective resident may review the public files described in subsection (e) of this section; and
The name, address, and phone number of the State or local ombudsman.
